MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"object’s progress changes. The progress may change due to a resource being","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"downloaded or because the pack discovers during the download that more","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"resources are required for offline viewing. This notification is posted","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"whenever any field in the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"progress"},{"type":"text","text":" property changes."}],"title":"MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol"}}}